<item>
            <title>[SPARK-12160] spark.mllib should use SQLContext.getOrCreate</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-12160</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;spark.mllib currently uses &lt;tt&gt;new SQLContext(...)&lt;/tt&gt; in several places, especially the model save/load methods.  It should use SQLContext.getOrCreate, which was introduced in Spark 1.4.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This can cause some problems, depending on how the user/system manages contexts.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
